01:02 look how exhausted Jungkook is, but he's still not satisfied with his performance... that hurts my heart! even more, these days, when people say he would be disrespectful, because his long hair would look messy... 😡 How can someone dare to say that Jungkook doesn't do enough for his fans!? He is the center of BTS and put unhuman effort in his performance. He endures exhaustion, pain, reluctance, hard rehearsals and daily exercise, too little sleep, hunger and diets, jetlegs and so much more! I can only admire him a lot! I admire them all! Of course! They all have their individually struggles, but they push themselfes through them all.
I think their concerts are extremely demanding for them, but while performing on stage they get loud cheers of ARMY and an immediate reward. But the day after a concert is possibly harder, because they're in pain and there are no cheers. All those hours, days, weeks and months of exercising and rehearsals must be very tough. Because they have to activate their mental motivation...
